<text><body>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0225b22" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0225b23" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0225b24" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1248</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0225b25" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><note n="0225002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】享和元年刊長谷寺藏本，【甲】高山寺藏古寫本</note><cb:jhead>北方毘沙門天王隨軍護法真言</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0225b26" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0225b27" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">特進試鴻臚卿大興善寺三藏沙門
<lb n="0225b28" ed="T"/>大廣智不空別行翻譯不入正經</byline>
<lb n="0225b29" ed="T"/><cb:div type="dharani"><p xml:id="pT21p0225b2901" cb:type="dharani"><note n="0225003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此梵字真言附載於卷末</note>曩謨囉多曩<note place="inline">二合</note>多羅<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0225004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔多〕－ヵ【原】</note><note n="0225004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">多【大】，〔－〕【考偽-原】</note><app n="0225004"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">多</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>夜耶阿馱佉路
<pb n="0225c" xml:id="T21.1248.0225c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0225c01" ed="T"/>步多囉<note place="inline">二合</note>耶地舍耶<note place="inline">二</note>吠室囉<note place="inline">二合</note>摩拏野<note place="inline">三</note>
<lb n="0225c02" ed="T"/>摩賀囉惹野<note place="inline">四</note>藥迦灑<note place="inline">二合</note>地婆多婆<note place="inline">五上</note>娑都
<lb n="0225c03" ed="T"/>哆娑娑室囉跛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>娑賀娜耶呬<note place="inline">賢二反</note>摩馱吒
<lb n="0225c04" ed="T"/>吒<note place="inline">去<note n="0225005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">呼＝乎【甲】</note><note n="0225005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">呼【大】，乎【甲】</note><app n="0225005"><lem wit="【大】">呼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">乎</rdg></app></note>尾跛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>灑夜迷跛娜也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note n="0225006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">保＝俁【甲】＊</note><note n="0225006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">保【大】＊，俁【甲】＊</note><app n="0225006"><lem wit="【大】">保</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">俁</rdg></app>
<lb n="0225c05" ed="T"/><g ref="#CB04048"/>儞<app type="star" corresp="#0225006"><lem wit="【大】">保</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">俁</rdg></app><g ref="#CB04048"/>儞俱沙吠室羅摩拏野摩賀囉惹
<lb n="0225c06" ed="T"/>耶綺<note place="inline">佉罽反</note>婆<note place="inline">去</note>馱伽儞多囉摩熾都麼麼<note place="inline">某甲受持</note>捺
<lb n="0225c07" ed="T"/>娑<note place="inline">上</note>娑馱耶娑那謨婆誐嚩帝悉殿都麼多囉
<lb n="0225c08" ed="T"/>跛馱儞娑婆<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0225c09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0225c0901">若行者受持此呪者。先須畫像。於彩色中並
<lb n="0225c10" ed="T"/>不得和膠。於白㲲上畫一毘沙門神。七寶莊
<lb n="0225c11" ed="T"/>嚴衣甲。左手執戟矟。右手<note n="0225007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">托＝託【甲】</note><note n="0225007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">托【大】，託【甲】</note><app n="0225007"><lem wit="【大】">托</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">託</rdg></app>腰上。其神脚
<lb n="0225c12" ed="T"/>下作二夜叉鬼。身並作黑色。其毘沙門面。作
<lb n="0225c13" ed="T"/>甚可畏形惡眼視一切鬼神勢。其塔奉釋迦
<lb n="0225c14" ed="T"/>牟尼佛。教汝若領天兵守界擁護國土。何護
<lb n="0225c15" ed="T"/>吾法。即擁遣第三子那吒捧行莫離其側。汝
<lb n="0225c16" ed="T"/>眼毒惡恐損眾生。爾時行者。若誦此呪時。就
<lb n="0225c17" ed="T"/>好地。勿使有穢惡之處。極令淨潔取牛糞塗
<lb n="0225c18" ed="T"/>地。即以香泥塗之。散種種花燒香供養。行者
<lb n="0225c19" ed="T"/>上下衣服。並須清淨一上廁一洗浴。白月十
<lb n="0225c20" ed="T"/>五日夜。起首對像前。誦呪滿十萬遍訖。然
<lb n="0225c21" ed="T"/>後更取香泥復塗壇上。更取上妙好花散壇
<lb n="0225c22" ed="T"/>中。設種種飲食。行者取薰陸香一百八顆。各
<lb n="0225c23" ed="T"/>呪一遍散著火中。爾時毘沙門即現其身。行
<lb n="0225c24" ed="T"/>者若見神時取上好食飲。供養毘沙門神通。
<lb n="0225c25" ed="T"/>行者心中所願其神悉見。若行者不見神時。
<lb n="0225c26" ed="T"/>即虛空中有聲<note n="0225008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">云＝告言ィ【原】</note><note n="0225008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">云【大】，告言【校異-原】</note><app n="0225008"><lem wit="【大】">云</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">告言</rdg></app>。汝但<note n="0225009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">存＝懃ィ【原】</note><note n="0225009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">存【大】，懃【校異-原】</note><app n="0225009"><lem wit="【大】">存</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">懃</rdg></app>心<note n="0225010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">持誦＝誦呪ィ【原】</note><note n="0225010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">持誦【大】，誦呪【校異-原】</note><app n="0225010"><lem wit="【大】">持誦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">誦呪</rdg></app>。一切
<lb n="0225c27" ed="T"/>事汝欲者悉如意。若不見神及不聞聲。但有
<lb n="0225c28" ed="T"/>大風。或雲遍滿布其壇上。其法即成就。若
<lb n="0225c29" ed="T"/>無上件等相。<note n="0225011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">行者＝更ィ【原】</note><note n="0225011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">行者【大】，更【校異-原】</note><app n="0225011"><lem wit="【大】">行者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">更</rdg></app>誦呪<note n="0225012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（一）ィ＋七【原】</note><note n="0225012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">七【大】，一七【校異-原】</note><app n="0225012"><lem wit="【大】">七</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">一七</rdg></app>遍。縛得<note n="0225013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">入＝人ィ【原】</note><note n="0225013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">入【大】，人【校異-原】</note><app n="0225013"><lem wit="【大】">入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">人</rdg></app>者
<pb n="0226a" xml:id="T21.1248.0226a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0226a01" ed="T"/>其法即成。更勿懷疑。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226a0109" cb:place="inline">又法若行者欲得喝
<lb n="0226a02" ed="T"/>囉闍愛敬者。取赤小豆一顆呪一遍。投火中
<lb n="0226a03" ed="T"/>燒。如是滿一百八遍。其喝囉闍即遣人<note n="0226001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">喚來極忽＝喚呪師如箭急急來ィ【原】</note><note n="0226001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">喚來極忽【大】，喚呪師如箭急急來【校異-原】</note><app n="0226001"><lem wit="【大】">喚
<lb n="0226a04" ed="T"/>來極忽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">喚呪師如箭急急來</rdg></app>。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226a0404" cb:place="inline">又法若欲得大<note n="0226002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">官＝印【甲】</note><note n="0226002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">官【大】，印【甲】</note><app n="0226002"><lem wit="【大】">官</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">印</rdg></app>人愛敬者。取
<lb n="0226a05" ed="T"/><note n="0226003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔白〕－【甲】</note><note n="0226003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">白【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0226003"><lem wit="【大】">白</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>芥子一顆。一呪投火中燒滿一百八遍。其
<lb n="0226a06" ed="T"/>官即自<note n="0226004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔來〕－【甲】</note><note n="0226004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">來【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0226004"><lem wit="【大】">來</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>敬仰大喜。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226a0609" cb:place="inline">又法於白月十五日
<lb n="0226a07" ed="T"/>作壇。於像前作八肘。牛糞塗地了。取香泥
<lb n="0226a08" ed="T"/>重塗了。以五色畫作三重院。其壇內於中畫
<lb n="0226a09" ed="T"/>一<note n="0226005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">大＝火ィ【原】</note><note n="0226005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大【大】，火【校異-原】</note><app n="0226005"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">火</rdg></app>輪。四角拔折羅十字安之。第二院內。
<lb n="0226a10" ed="T"/>東面畫作一火珠光焰<note n="0226006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">火＝上ィ【原】</note><note n="0226006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">火【大】，上【校異-原】</note><app n="0226006"><lem wit="【大】">火</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">上</rdg></app>出。南面畫三<note n="0226007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">股＝鈷【甲】</note><note n="0226007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">股【大】，鈷【甲】</note><app n="0226007"><lem wit="【大】">股</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">鈷</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0226a11" ed="T"/>又西面畫一龍口中<note n="0226008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">並＝著ィ【原】</note><note n="0226008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">並【大】，著【校異-原】</note><app n="0226008"><lem wit="【大】">並</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">著</rdg></app>出蓮華。北面畫一大
<lb n="0226a12" ed="T"/><note n="0226009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">縲＝螺ィ【原】</note><note n="0226009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">縲【大】，螺【校異-原】</note><app n="0226009"><lem wit="【大】">縲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">螺</rdg></app>。第三院中東面<note n="0226010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔更〕ィ－【原】</note><note n="0226010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">更【大】，〔－〕【校異-原】</note><app n="0226010"><lem wit="【大】">更</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>畫師子。南面畫龍
<lb n="0226a13" ed="T"/>王。西面畫孔雀王<note n="0226011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔鳥〕ィ－【原】</note><note n="0226011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鳥【大】，〔－〕【校異-原】</note><app n="0226011"><lem wit="【大】">鳥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。北面畫<note n="0226012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">羅剎手＝夜叉王ィ【原】</note><note n="0226012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">羅剎手【大】，夜叉王【校異-原】</note><app n="0226012"><lem wit="【大】">羅剎手</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">夜叉王</rdg></app>拄<note n="0226013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">棒＝杖ィ【原】</note><note n="0226013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">棒【大】，杖【校異-原】</note><app n="0226013"><lem wit="【大】">棒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">杖</rdg></app>
<lb n="0226a14" ed="T"/>立地。壇四角各安香水瓶。內著雜菓楊枝。呪
<lb n="0226a15" ed="T"/>師洗浴著新淨衣。於像前設種種飲食供養。
<lb n="0226a16" ed="T"/>即誦呪取呵梨勒<note n="0226014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">一顆＝一百八顆ィ【原】</note><note n="0226014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一顆【大】，一百八顆【校異-原】</note><app n="0226014"><lem wit="【大】">一顆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">一百八顆</rdg></app>。一呪一遍投火中燒
<lb n="0226a17" ed="T"/>之。滿一百八遍。從今已後。每日送一<note n="0226015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB04123"/>＝送金一鋋ィ【原】，鎰ヵ【原】</note><note n="0226015" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><g ref="#CB04123"/>【大】，送金一鋋【校異-原】，鎰【考偽-原】</note><app n="0226015"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】"><g ref="#CB04123"/></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">送金一鋋</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">鎰</rdg></app>金
<lb n="0226a18" ed="T"/>與呪師永無乏少。若得此物即須用盡。不得
<lb n="0226a19" ed="T"/>留著。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226a1903" cb:place="inline">又法呪蘇蜜及菓子。一百八遍火中
<lb n="0226a20" ed="T"/>燒之。一切諸天皆大歡喜擁護呪師。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226a2015" cb:place="inline">又法
<lb n="0226a21" ed="T"/>若欲遠行時。呪穀木<note n="0226016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">柱＝拄杖ィ【原】</note><note n="0226016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">柱【大】，拄杖【校異-原】</note><app n="0226016"><lem wit="【大】">柱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">拄杖</rdg></app>行一切難處。悉得
<lb n="0226a22" ed="T"/>無怖。又法若惡人相惱亂者。心中想此呪
<lb n="0226a23" ed="T"/>神形。復舉心誦呪。未滿一遍。其人即不能
<lb n="0226a24" ed="T"/><note n="0226017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（行）ィ＋動【原】</note><note n="0226017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">動【大】，行動【校異-原】</note><app n="0226017"><lem wit="【大】">動</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">行動</rdg></app>。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226a2402" cb:place="inline">若欲好者。心放中相<note n="0226018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">便＋（云即）【甲】</note><note n="0226018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便【大】，便云即【甲】</note><app n="0226018"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">便云即</rdg></app>得解脫。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226a2414" cb:place="inline">又
<lb n="0226a25" ed="T"/>法若欲令怨家<note n="0226019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">不同住＝遠相却ィ【原】</note><note n="0226019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不同住【大】，遠相却【校異-原】</note><app n="0226019"><lem wit="【大】">不同住</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">遠相却</rdg></app>者。取苦練<note n="0226020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">子＝木ィ【原】</note><note n="0226020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">子【大】，木【校異-原】</note><app n="0226020"><lem wit="【大】">子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">木</rdg></app>一百
<lb n="0226a26" ed="T"/>八顆。一呪<note n="0226021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（一）＋投【甲】</note><note n="0226021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">投【大】，一投【甲】</note><app n="0226021"><lem wit="【大】">投</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">一投</rdg></app>火中。其人即自遠去。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226a2614" cb:place="inline">又法
<lb n="0226a27" ed="T"/>若呪胡麻一百八遍。散著火中。一切人盡來
<lb n="0226a28" ed="T"/>供養呪師。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226a2805" cb:place="inline">又法若呪白芥子一百八遍散山
<lb n="0226a29" ed="T"/>中。一切惡獸不能傷人。其<note n="0226022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">狩＝獸ヵ【原】</note><note n="0226022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">狩【大】，獸【考偽-原】</note><app n="0226022"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">狩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">獸</rdg></app>見人即自伏
<pb n="0226b" xml:id="T21.1248.0226b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0226b01" ed="T"/>地不敢傷害。過去已後方即起去。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226b0114" cb:place="inline">又法若
<lb n="0226b02" ed="T"/>欲乞雨時。<note n="0226023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔取〕－【甲】</note><note n="0226023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">取【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0226023"><lem wit="【大】">取</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>杏<note n="0226024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">子＋（人）【原】</note><note n="0226024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">子【大】，子人【原】</note><app n="0226024"><lem wit="【大】">子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】">子人</rdg></app>一百八顆都呪三七遍。
<lb n="0226b03" ed="T"/>著有龍水中必得雨下。欲止雨時。取梧桐子
<lb n="0226b04" ed="T"/>火中燒之即止。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226b0407" cb:place="inline">又法若行者欲乞食。先呪
<lb n="0226b05" ed="T"/>鉢一百八遍。隨所<note n="0226025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">到＝致【甲】</note><note n="0226025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">到【大】，致【甲】</note><app n="0226025"><lem wit="【大】">到</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">致</rdg></app>處。自然而得一切飲
<lb n="0226b06" ed="T"/>食了。飲<note n="0226026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔食〕－【甲】</note><note n="0226026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0226026"><lem wit="【大】">食</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>殘者當時自化<note n="0226027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">去＝土【甲】</note><note n="0226027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">去【大】，土【甲】</note><app n="0226027"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">土</rdg></app>。若須飲食時。
<lb n="0226b07" ed="T"/>至心向鉢<note n="0226028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔者〕ィ－【原】</note><note n="0226028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">者【大】，〔－〕【校異-原】</note><app n="0226028"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>誦呪一遍。其鉢依還如故。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226b0716" cb:place="inline">又
<lb n="0226b08" ed="T"/>法若欲見功<note n="0226029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">能＝德【甲】＊</note><note n="0226029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">能【大】＊，德【甲】＊</note><app n="0226029"><lem wit="【大】">能</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">德</rdg></app>天者。一日一夜不食。於佛
<lb n="0226b09" ed="T"/>前燒蘇合香。呪白花一百八遍。以散<note n="0226030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">神＝佛ィ【原】</note><note n="0226030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">神【大】，佛【校異-原】</note><app n="0226030"><lem wit="【大】">神</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">佛</rdg></app>前。
<lb n="0226b10" ed="T"/>其功<app type="star" corresp="#0226029"><lem wit="【大】">能</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">德</rdg></app>天即自現身。隨意所須一切願滿。所
<lb n="0226b11" ed="T"/>求財寶即得稱意。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226b1108" cb:place="inline">若欲<note n="0226031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">辟＝避ィ【原】</note><note n="0226031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">辟【大】，避【校異-原】</note><app n="0226031"><lem wit="【大】">辟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">避</rdg></app>除一切鬼神。呪
<lb n="0226b12" ed="T"/>白芥子及蘇。呪一顆一遍。投火中燒之即得。</p>
<lb n="0226b13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0226b1301">若有<note n="0226032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">官＝惡ィ【原】</note><note n="0226032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">官【大】，惡【校異-原】</note><app n="0226032"><lem wit="【大】">官</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">惡</rdg></app>人。於三寶<note n="0226033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">中＝所ィ【原】</note><note n="0226033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">中【大】，所【校異-原】</note><app n="0226033"><lem wit="【大】">中</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">所</rdg></app>起不善心者。惱亂
<lb n="0226b14" ed="T"/>佛弟子者。欲令起慈心。須作降伏。呪手<note n="0226034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三＝二ィ【原】</note><note n="0226034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三【大】，二【校異-原】</note><app n="0226034"><lem wit="【大】">三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">二</rdg></app>
<lb n="0226b15" ed="T"/>十一遍。遙打之其人即著疾。欲<note n="0226035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">好＝改ィ【原】</note><note n="0226035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">好【大】，改【校異-原】</note><app n="0226035"><lem wit="【大】">好</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">改</rdg></app>者慈心
<lb n="0226b16" ed="T"/>誦一遍即差。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226b1606" cb:place="inline">又法呪土二十一遍。散自身
<lb n="0226b17" ed="T"/>上。一切人<note n="0226036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">見＋（者）ィ【原】</note><note n="0226036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見【大】，見者【校異-原】</note><app n="0226036"><lem wit="【大】">見</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">見者</rdg></app>無不敬仰。欲令自身有威光
<lb n="0226b18" ed="T"/>者。呪墨塗額上。一切人見者無不愛仰。呪
<lb n="0226b19" ed="T"/>灰二十一遍。塗其身大眾中一切人<note n="0226037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">見＝者【甲】</note><note n="0226037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見【大】，者【甲】</note><app n="0226037"><lem wit="【大】">見</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">者</rdg></app>皆福
<lb n="0226b20" ed="T"/>德相。眾人供養。欲得遠涉道路不被惡人
<lb n="0226b21" ed="T"/>惡<note n="0226038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">狩＝獸ィ【原】</note><note n="0226038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">狩【大】，獸【校異-原】</note><app n="0226038"><lem wit="【大】">狩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">獸</rdg></app>傷害。行<note n="0226039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">加＝如ヵ【原】</note><note n="0226039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">加【大】，如【考偽-原】</note><app n="0226039"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">加</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">如</rdg></app>奔馬。呪左<note n="0226040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">手＋（以四指握）ィ【原】</note><note n="0226040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">手【大】，手以四指握【校異-原】</note><app n="0226040"><lem wit="【大】">手</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">手以四指握</rdg></app>大母指作
<lb n="0226b22" ed="T"/><note n="0226041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">印＝拳ィ【原】</note><note n="0226041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">印【大】，拳【校異-原】</note><app n="0226041"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">拳</rdg></app>。而去欲得於鏡看事。呪童<note n="0226042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">子＝男ィ【原】</note><note n="0226042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">子【大】，男【校異-原】</note><app n="0226042"><lem wit="【大】">子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">男</rdg></app>童女問吉
<lb n="0226b23" ed="T"/>凶。其人即自下語。令道所病鬼姓名。即知
<lb n="0226b24" ed="T"/>是何等之病。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226b2406" cb:place="inline">若被<note n="0226043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蠱＝蟲ィ【原】</note><note n="0226043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蠱【大】，蟲【校異-原】</note><app n="0226043"><lem wit="【大】">蠱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">蟲</rdg></app>毒食者。呪所食物二
<lb n="0226b25" ed="T"/>十一遍。其所為毒即吐出。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226b2511" cb:place="inline">若患鬼病呪五
<lb n="0226b26" ed="T"/>色線。一遍一結一百八遍了。繫頭上或頂上
<lb n="0226b27" ed="T"/>臂上。一切病患除差。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226b2709" cb:place="inline">若患心<note n="0226044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">病＝痛ィ【原】＊</note><note n="0226044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">病【大】＊，痛【校異-原】＊</note><app n="0226044"><lem wit="【大】">病</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">痛</rdg></app>。呪石榴
<lb n="0226b28" ed="T"/><note n="0226045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔花〕－【甲】</note><note n="0226045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">花【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0226045"><lem wit="【大】">花</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>汁飲之即愈。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226b2807" cb:place="inline">若欲攝<note n="0226046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">狐魅＝野狐ィ【原】</note><note n="0226046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">狐魅【大】，野狐【校異-原】</note><app n="0226046"><lem wit="【大】">狐魅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">野狐</rdg></app>病。呪五色
<lb n="0226b29" ed="T"/>線。令童<note n="0226047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">子＝女ィ【原】</note><note n="0226047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">子【大】，女【校異-原】</note><app n="0226047"><lem wit="【大】">子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">女</rdg></app>合<note n="0226048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔成〕ィ－【原】</note><note n="0226048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">成【大】，〔－〕【校異-原】</note><app n="0226048"><lem wit="【大】">成</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>索。一呪一結一百八遍。繫
<pb n="0226c" xml:id="T21.1248.0226c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0226c01" ed="T"/><note n="0226049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">項＝頸【甲】</note><note n="0226049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">項【大】，頸【甲】</note><app n="0226049"><lem wit="【大】">項</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">頸</rdg></app>下。<note n="0226050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">復＝更ィ【原】</note><note n="0226050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">復【大】，更【校異-原】</note><app n="0226050"><lem wit="【大】">復</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">更</rdg></app>呪楊枝打病者即立愈。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226c0113" cb:place="inline">若患骨
<lb n="0226c02" ed="T"/>節<note n="0226051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔楚〕ィ－【原】</note><note n="0226051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">楚【大】，〔－〕【校異-原】</note><app n="0226051"><lem wit="【大】">楚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>病。呪<note n="0226052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">宥＝鎖鐵ィ【原】</note><note n="0226052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">宥【大】，鎖鐵【校異-原】</note><app n="0226052"><lem wit="【大】">宥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">鎖鐵</rdg></app>刀禁其病即愈。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226c0212" cb:place="inline">若欲護身。
<lb n="0226c03" ed="T"/>呪白芥子二十一遍。若灰若水亦然。散四方
<lb n="0226c04" ed="T"/>為界。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226c0403" cb:place="inline">若頭<app type="star" corresp="#0226044"><lem wit="【大】">病</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">痛</rdg></app>或身病呪蘇烏麻油二十一
<lb n="0226c05" ed="T"/>遍。摩塗其身即愈。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226c0508" cb:place="inline">若患耳風呪蘇二十一
<lb n="0226c06" ed="T"/>遍食之愈。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226c0605" cb:place="inline">若患眼。呪杏人油塗之立愈。</p>
<lb n="0226c07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0226c0701">若患腫。呪石榴<note n="0226053" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">黃＝及黃檀香ィ【原】</note><note n="0226053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">黃【大】，及黃檀香【校異-原】</note><app n="0226053"><lem wit="【大】">黃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">及黃檀香</rdg></app>一百八遍塗上即愈。或白
<lb n="0226c08" ed="T"/>檀香亦得。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226c0805" cb:place="inline">若患頭<note n="0226054" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">病＝頂ィ【原】</note><note n="0226054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">病【大】，頂【校異-原】</note><app n="0226054"><lem wit="【大】">病</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">頂</rdg></app>。呪大黃二十一遍。塗
<lb n="0226c09" ed="T"/>額上即愈。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226c0905" cb:place="inline">若患時氣病。呪青木香末二十
<lb n="0226c10" ed="T"/>一遍。和水服之立愈。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226c1009" cb:place="inline">若患惡瘡疥癬者。取
<lb n="0226c11" ed="T"/>利蘆<note n="0226055" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">未＝末ィ【原】，木【甲】</note><note n="0226055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">未【大】，末【校異-原】，木【甲】</note><app n="0226055"><lem wit="【大】">未</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">末</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">木</rdg></app>和油塗上立即除愈。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226c1112" cb:place="inline">若患瘧病。呪
<lb n="0226c12" ed="T"/>楊枝二十一遍<note n="0226056" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">令打病人＝令病人把【甲】</note><note n="0226056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">令打病人【大】，令病人把【甲】</note><app n="0226056"><lem wit="【大】">令打病人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">令病人把</rdg></app>即時除愈。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226c1215" cb:place="inline">若被
<lb n="0226c13" ed="T"/>蝎<note n="0226057" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">螫＝赦【甲】</note><note n="0226057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">螫【大】，赦【甲】</note><app n="0226057"><lem wit="【大】">螫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">赦</rdg></app>。呪乾脯火中<note n="0226058" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">燒之熱＝熱燒ィ【原】</note><note n="0226058" resp="CBETA" type="mod">燒之熱【大】，熱燒【校異-原】</note><app n="0226058"><lem wit="【大】">燒之。熱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">熱燒</rdg></app>拄其上便即除
<lb n="0226c14" ed="T"/>愈。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226c1402" cb:place="inline">若被蛇咬。呪畢<note n="0226059" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鉢＝撥枝ィ【原】</note><note n="0226059" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鉢【大】，撥枝【校異-原】</note><app n="0226059"><lem wit="【大】">鉢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">撥枝</rdg></app>二十一遍。塗之當下
<lb n="0226c15" ed="T"/>即愈。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226c1503" cb:place="inline">若婦人乳腫。呪油麻嚼塗上即差。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226c1516" cb:place="inline">若
<lb n="0226c16" ed="T"/>帶下病者。呪<note n="0226060" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔丁〕ィ－【原】</note><note n="0226060" resp="CBETA" type="mod">丁【大】，〔－〕【校異-原】</note><app n="0226060"><lem wit="【大】">丁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>香水服之<note n="0226061" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔即愈〕－【甲】</note><note n="0226061" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即愈【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0226061"><lem wit="【大】">即愈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226c1613" cb:place="inline">若人卒
<lb n="0226c17" ed="T"/>被鬼著狂言荒語。呪水<note n="0226062" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">令＝含ィ【原】</note><note n="0226062" resp="CBETA" type="mod">令【大】，含【校異-原】</note><app n="0226062"><lem wit="【大】">令</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">含</rdg></app><note n="0226063" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">服之＝其服ィ【原】</note><note n="0226063" resp="CBETA" type="mod">服之【大】，其服【校異-原】</note><app n="0226063"><lem wit="【大】">服之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">其服</rdg></app>。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226c1713" cb:place="inline">若患心
<lb n="0226c18" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0226044"><lem wit="【大】">病</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">痛</rdg></app>。呪黃土塗之。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226c1807" cb:place="inline">若患一切鬼<note n="0226064" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">魅＋（病）ィ【原】</note><note n="0226064" resp="CBETA" type="mod">魅【大】，魅病【校異-原】</note><app n="0226064"><lem wit="【大】">魅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">魅病</rdg></app>者。呪石
<lb n="0226c19" ed="T"/>榴枝一百八遍。用打病者即愈。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0226c1913" cb:place="inline">若欲得成
<lb n="0226c20" ed="T"/>就三事者。當於像前作壇。壇內散種種名花。
<pb n="0227a" xml:id="T21.1248.0227a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0227a01" ed="T"/>設種種飲食訖。取赤銅鈝一枚。雄黃三兩細
<lb n="0227a02" ed="T"/>擣和蜜水為丸置像前。取荷葉覆上。以手掩
<lb n="0227a03" ed="T"/>之呪不息。當有相現。若烟出時取塗身上。即
<lb n="0227a04" ed="T"/>成安怛陀那。若火出時。手取火焰用塗面上。
<lb n="0227a05" ed="T"/>一切眾生見此人者皆大歡喜敬仰有大威
<lb n="0227a06" ed="T"/>光。所出言教人皆信受恭敬隨順。若有煖氣
<lb n="0227a07" ed="T"/>其人即取塗身即得無盡。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0227a0711" cb:place="inline">又法於舍利塔前
<lb n="0227a08" ed="T"/>呪牛黃。依前藥法皆得塗身一切福德盡集
<lb n="0227a09" ed="T"/>其身。所在眾生見如羅闍無異。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0227a0913" cb:place="inline">又法<note n="0227001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">若＋（欲）ィ【原】</note><note n="0227001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">若【大】，若欲【校異-原】</note><app n="0227001"><lem wit="【大】">若</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">若欲</rdg></app>知
<lb n="0227a10" ed="T"/>山間有孔似阿修羅窟者。當呪白芥子和自
<lb n="0227a11" ed="T"/>身血。一呪一遍打山間孔。盡一千八遍。其山
<lb n="0227a12" ed="T"/>窟自開。其阿修羅女身如火然。持諸香花<note n="0227002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">迎＝及ィ【原】，取【甲】</note><note n="0227002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">迎【大】，及【校異-原】，取【甲】</note><app n="0227002"><lem wit="【大】">迎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">及</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">取</rdg></app>
<lb n="0227a13" ed="T"/>呪師來。行者入此窟內。壽命一大劫身力還
<lb n="0227a14" ed="T"/>如阿修羅。亦如金剛無能損者。若欲出時亦
<lb n="0227a15" ed="T"/>得一切阿修羅女隨從。若不還時亦到<note n="0227003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">火＝大【甲】</note><note n="0227003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">火【大】，大【甲】</note><app n="0227003"><lem wit="【大】">火</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">大</rdg></app>終
<lb n="0227a16" ed="T"/>無所害。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0227a1604" cb:place="inline">又法將此像向舍利塔前。香塗地
<lb n="0227a17" ed="T"/>香花散於壇內。上妙供養了。取梨木作合子。
<lb n="0227a18" ed="T"/>取安膳那石為末。用秦膠水為丸。盛於合子
<lb n="0227a19" ed="T"/>中置壇中。行者著新淨衣。在於像前一日不
<lb n="0227a20" ed="T"/>食。誦此呪一千八遍<note n="0227004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">了＝竟ィ【原】</note><note n="0227004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">了【大】，竟【校異-原】</note><app n="0227004"><lem wit="【大】">了</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">竟</rdg></app>。亦無勞三相現。呪
<lb n="0227a21" ed="T"/>一千八遍訖<note n="0227005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">塗＝用【甲】</note><note n="0227005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">塗【大】，用【甲】</note><app n="0227005"><lem wit="【大】">塗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">用</rdg></app>眼竟。<note n="0227006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">即＝亦ィ【原】</note><note n="0227006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即【大】，亦【校異-原】</note><app n="0227006"><lem wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">亦</rdg></app>塗脚<note n="0227007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">掌＝常【甲】</note><note n="0227007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">掌【大】，常【甲】</note><app n="0227007"><lem wit="【大】">掌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">常</rdg></app>心中胸前
<lb n="0227a22" ed="T"/>兩膊上<note n="0227008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔頂〕ィ－【原】</note><note n="0227008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">頂【大】，〔－〕【校異-原】</note><app n="0227008"><lem wit="【大】">頂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>竟。至心合掌思身如虛空。無有
<lb n="0227a23" ed="T"/>身相作<note n="0227009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">自＝此ィ【原】</note><note n="0227009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">自【大】，此【校異-原】</note><app n="0227009"><lem wit="【大】">自</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">此</rdg></app>想時。行者隱形日行千里。一切事
<lb n="0227a24" ed="T"/>業竝皆悉見。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0227a2406" cb:place="inline">又法欲得伏外道入火中。取自
<lb n="0227a25" ed="T"/>身血魚血。瞋心誦此呪二十一遍。投火中即
<lb n="0227a26" ed="T"/>入火中。<note n="0227010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">得一頃食＝經一食頃ィ【原】</note><note n="0227010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得一頃食【大】，經一食頃【校異-原】</note><app n="0227010"><lem wit="【大】">得一頃食</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">經一食頃</rdg></app>間不燒其身。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0227a2613" cb:place="inline">又法若欲
<lb n="0227a27" ed="T"/>降伏外道。手中結印。瞋心誦呪一百八遍。外
<lb n="0227a28" ed="T"/>道所作法悉破壞竝不成就。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0227a2812" cb:place="inline">又法若欲降伏
<lb n="0227a29" ed="T"/>諸國兵賊眾者。當畫一像身卦紫磨真金甲。
<pb n="0227b" xml:id="T21.1248.0227b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0227b01" ed="T"/>於淨室中燒眾名香乳頭薰陸香。諸色香花
<lb n="0227b02" ed="T"/>飲食供養。<note n="0227011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">真＝瞋ィ【原】</note><note n="0227011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">真【大】，瞋【校異-原】</note><app n="0227011"><lem wit="【大】">真</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">瞋</rdg></app>心誦念天王真言十萬遍。天王
<lb n="0227b03" ed="T"/>領天兵來助。他國兵敵自退散。若能晝夜誦
<lb n="0227b04" ed="T"/>念不絕。天王使太子獨健。領天兵千人衛護
<lb n="0227b05" ed="T"/>不離其側。所求如意應念隨心。皆得成就。</p>
<lb n="0227b06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0227b0601">又法若欲降前敵眾者。於淨室持齋畫一天
<lb n="0227b07" ed="T"/>王形像。卦紫磨真金甲。於二丈竿懸。軍前五
<lb n="0227b08" ed="T"/>十步指其敵。其敵不能相患。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0227b0812" cb:place="inline">印相二小指
<lb n="0227b09" ed="T"/><note n="0227012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔相〕－【甲】</note><note n="0227012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">相【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0227012"><lem wit="【大】">相</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>鉤。二無名指向外直豎。二中指<note n="0227013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二頭指〕－【甲】</note><note n="0227013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二頭指【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0227013"><lem wit="【大】">二頭指</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0227b10" ed="T"/>反相叉。二大母<note n="0227014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔指〕－【甲】</note><note n="0227014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">指【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0227014"><lem wit="【大】">指</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>向外直豎。手掌<note n="0227015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">背合＝相背ィ【原】，〔背〕－【甲】</note><note n="0227015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">背合【大】，相背【校異-原】，合【甲】</note><app n="0227015"><lem wit="【大】">背合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">相背</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">合</rdg></app>即
<lb n="0227b11" ed="T"/>是其印。如前所說一一諸法。皆用此印即得
<lb n="0227b12" ed="T"/>成就。今我說根本印。以二手右押左內相
<lb n="0227b13" ed="T"/>叉。豎無<note n="0227016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">名＋（指）ィ【原】</note><note n="0227016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">名【大】，名指【校異-原】</note><app n="0227016"><lem wit="【大】">名</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">名指</rdg></app>頭相<note n="0227017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">合＋（屈）ィ【原】</note><note n="0227017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">合【大】，合屈【校異-原】</note><app n="0227017"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">合屈</rdg></app>。二頭指<note n="0227018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔屈〕ィ－【原】</note><note n="0227018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">屈【大】，〔－〕【校異-原】</note><app n="0227018"><lem wit="【大】">屈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>如鉤。若迎
<lb n="0227b14" ed="T"/>請時向身招。若<note n="0227019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">撥＝發【甲】</note><note n="0227019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">撥【大】，發【甲】</note><app n="0227019"><lem wit="【大】">撥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">發</rdg></app>遣時<note n="0227020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（向）ィ＋外【原】</note><note n="0227020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">外【大】，向外【校異-原】</note><app n="0227020"><lem wit="【大】">外</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">向外</rdg></app>撥。念<note n="0227021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">請＝誦ィ【原】</note><note n="0227021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">請【大】，誦【校異-原】</note><app n="0227021"><lem wit="【大】">請</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">誦</rdg></app>時結印
<lb n="0227b15" ed="T"/>當心誦七遍。<note n="0227022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">印＝即ィ【原】</note><note n="0227022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">印【大】，即【校異-原】</note><app n="0227022"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">即</rdg></app>頂上散。然後取念珠專<note n="0227023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">住＝注ィ【原】</note><note n="0227023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">住【大】，注【校異-原】</note><app n="0227023"><lem wit="【大】">住</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">注</rdg></app>
<lb n="0227b16" ed="T"/>念誦。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0227b1603" cb:place="inline">次說吉祥天<note n="0227024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">女＋（身）ィ【原】</note><note n="0227024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">女【大】，女身【校異-原】</note><app n="0227024"><lem wit="【大】">女</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">女身</rdg></app>印。<note n="0227025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔以〕ィ－【原】</note><note n="0227025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以【大】，〔－〕【校異-原】</note><app n="0227025"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>二手虛心合
<lb n="0227b17" ed="T"/>掌開二頭指二中指二無名指。<note n="0227026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔未〕ィ－【原】</note><note n="0227026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">未【大】，〔－〕【校異-原】</note><app n="0227026"><lem wit="【大】">未</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>屈如蓮華
<lb n="0227b18" ed="T"/>形。二大指二小指豎合。若念<note n="0227027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">誦＋（時）ィ【原】</note><note n="0227027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">誦【大】，誦時【校異-原】</note><app n="0227027"><lem wit="【大】">誦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">誦時</rdg></app>當心結<note n="0227028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔印〕－【甲】</note><note n="0227028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">印【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0227028"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。
<lb n="0227b19" ed="T"/>誦真言七遍頂上散印。四天王經云。若有人
<lb n="0227b20" ed="T"/>誦念此北方毘沙門天王真言。供養苽菓飲
<lb n="0227b21" ed="T"/>食。每月取一十五日二十一日。音聲用單雙
<lb n="0227b22" ed="T"/>絃方響鼓舞。蘇蜜乳粥真心誦念其天王即
<lb n="0227b23" ed="T"/>見其身隨心所願。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0227b24" ed="T"/><cb:div type="w"><p xml:id="pT21p0227b2401">解穢陀羅尼。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0227b2406" cb:type="dharani" cb:place="inline">唵俱嚕馱唵<g ref="#CB03928"/></p><p xml:id="pT21p0227b2412" cb:place="inline">讚天王頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0227b25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0227b2501">善利萬物兮惟彼水方　護持國界兮惟我
<lb n="0227b26" ed="T"/>天王　良將受委兮鎮固封彊　精心奉職
<lb n="0227b27" ed="T"/>兮宣託福祥　星宮上勝兮迴架崇岡　靈
<lb n="0227b28" ed="T"/>像儼立兮眾寶嚴莊　威神震曜兮攝伏荒
<lb n="0227b29" ed="T"/>保　又忠貞□兮<note n="0227029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">翅＝翊ィ【甲】</note><note n="0227029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">翅【大】，翊【校異-甲】</note><app n="0227029"><lem wit="【大】">翅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">翊</rdg></app>贊聖<note n="0227030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此次行甲本有毘沙門儀軌五字</note>唐</p>
<pb n="0227c" xml:id="T21.1248.0227c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0227c01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0227c0101"><note n="0227031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以下甲本無之</note><note n="0227031" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: a-->以下甲本無之</note>圓行錄云。北方毘沙門天王隨軍護法真
<lb n="0227c02" ed="T"/>言一卷。不空三藏別行翻譯。八家錄亦爾
<lb n="0227c03" ed="T"/>也。此法請寫於智山慈順僧正染筆。栂尾
<lb n="0227c04" ed="T"/>山之本。愛染院大宣等對挍之。予亦挍閱
<lb n="0227c05" ed="T"/>以上本。</p>
<lb n="0227c06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0227c0601">　時享和辛酉八月　　長谷僧快道誌</p>
<lb n="0227c07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0227c0701">　一校加筆畢　　　　　　　　慈順</p>
